cs.AR, cs.AI, cs.SY, cs.SE, cs.DC

Reasoning: 
- cs.AR (Architecture): The paper proposes a benchmarking methodology and framework for designing and evaluating hardware and software architectures for AI applications. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The paper focuses on benchmarking AI tasks and proposes an AI benchmark suite. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control): The paper discusses end-to-end application scenarios and proposes a methodology for building end-to-end benchmarks, which involves system-level considerations. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering): The paper proposes a flexible and configurable benchmark framework, which is relevant to software engineering. 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing): The paper mentions big data and internet services, which are often associated with distributed and parallel computing.
